    <briefdescription>
<para>Helper macros for the C/C++ preprocessor. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Utilities for macro expansion and safe forwarding of tokens.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Building blocks for more complex preprocessor metaprogramming patterns.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Designed to be portable and minimal. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
